&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Compliance Team has a very special role in our mission: support the company’s growth by identifying the Compliance risks that Nu faces; designing and implementing controls to protect Nu from such risks; and by providing advisory to the Business on regulations and internal policies to create the best product or service that follows with these external and internal standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are searching for a Compliance Specialist to work with Crypto and Blockchain themes, including the definition of action plans to comply with regulatory requirements and deadlines, prevention and detection of anomalies that may result in gaps. It is also expected that this position supports other themes in Compliance, related to AML, fraud and FX regulatory requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position requires working and interfacing with multiple partners and teams, evaluating new regulations and supporting business areas, giving regulatory advisories about product and procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
