&lt;li&gt;Monitor and answer inquiries from the regulators;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the Compliance team with the regulatory tests;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support to business areas, giving regulatory advisories about products and procedures;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prevention and detection of anomalies that may result in regulatory gaps;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Registration of action plans to comply with regulatory requirements and deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To evaluate possible conflict of interests, when applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
