&lt;li&gt;Capacity to deeply analyze new rules and understand its impacts, being hungry to go after information and seeking knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear and objective communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiation and organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing skills and objectiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on approach and ownership mentality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other skills: the candidate needs to be open and flexible with possible rotation of topics inside the Team; Help with the team&#39;s cross demands may be needed; Performing operational activities that are part of the team&#39;s routines may be needed.&lt;/li&gt;
