&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Own the &lt;strong&gt;end‑to‑end design and evolution&lt;/strong&gt; of ERM methodologies, ensuring coherence across programs and geographies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure ERM methodologies &lt;strong&gt;connect across risk types&lt;/strong&gt; (e.g., operational, compliance, technology, conduct, model, financial/credit where relevant) and support a consistent view of the risk profile.&lt;/p&gt;
