&lt;p&gt;Translate methodological requirements into &lt;strong&gt;GRC platform, product and data specifications&lt;/strong&gt;, partnering with Platform and engineering teams to build scalable, intuitive workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
