&lt;p&gt;Lead the &lt;strong&gt;global standardization&lt;/strong&gt; of global ERM methodologies while enabling smart local adaptations to meet regulatory expectations in each geo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Design and drive the &lt;strong&gt;integration of ERM programs in new geos&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring that new launches start already aligned with group‑level risk standards and governance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Define and embed &lt;strong&gt;AI/agent use‑cases&lt;/strong&gt; into ERM workflows (e.g., risk/control suggestions, narrative pre‑population, quality checks), with clear human‑in‑the‑loop governance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use AI and analytics to &lt;strong&gt;monitor quality and consistency&lt;/strong&gt; of methodologies, surfacing insights and opportunities for continuous improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with risk leaders (financial and non-financial risks), CRO teams, risk stewards and 1LOD to ensure &lt;strong&gt;strong adoption&lt;/strong&gt; and practical usability of ERM frameworks in day‑to‑day decision making.&lt;/p&gt;
