&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Independently manage discussions with a range of stakeholders across Engineering, Product, Risk, and Finance — bringing new ideas and driving the team toward innovative and efficient solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for a person who has&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Experienced level in financial analysis, accounting, compliance, and controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Stack:&lt;/strong&gt; Proficiency in SQL, Python, and/or Scala. Experienced in data analysis, visualization, and building insightful dashboards tailored to different stakeholder needs. Familiarity with data orchestration tools.&lt;/li&gt;
