&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Nubank, AI is not a &quot;bolt on&quot; feature. It is existential to our next phase of growth. We are transforming into an AI native company, where intelligent systems don&#39;t just support our products; they define them. As a Lead Software Engineer in AI Agents &amp;amp; Orchestration, you will be at the heart of this metamorphosis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead the technical direction for embedding Generative AI and LLMs into the lives of over 130 million customers. This role isn&#39;t about working in an isolated lab; it&#39;s about building production grade, agentic workflows and RAG pipelines that scale across multiple markets. You will leverage our specialized GenAI Platform including: inference services, evaluation frameworks, and orchestration layers to move from experimentation to global impact at &quot;Nu-speed.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why this role is compelling&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agency &amp;amp; Transformation: You aren&#39;t just a cog in a machine; you are an architect of the AI Native Bank.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale that Matters: Your code will power financial empowerment for a population larger than most countries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The AI Multiplier: You will work within a formal framework that measures and rewards the productivity gains and innovation you unlock via AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
