&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the AI Architecture: Define the technical roadmap for AI native applications, ensuring our LLM integrations are scalable, cost effective, and highly reliable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build Agentic Workflows: Design and implement complex agentic systems and RAG patterns that provide hyper-personalized financial experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive Engineering Excellence: Set the &quot;canonical&quot; standards for AI development at Nu, promoting reusable components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate Across Surfaces: Partner with Product, Design, and Data Science to embed LLM capabilities across mobile, web, and internal operations tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize for Quality: Establish rigorous evaluation (QA) and monitoring practices for AI outputs to ensure safety, accuracy, and human in the loop integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and Scale: Actively participate in hiring and mentoring, fostering a high performance culture within our internal AI Academy and technical guilds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Decision Making: Balance short term delivery with medium term platform stability, making critical tradeoffs on model selection and system complexity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
